								</li>

								</li>

								   <a href="http://newsroom.ucla.edu/releases/ucla-chemists-synthesize-narrow-ribbons-of-graphene-for-next-generation-electronics">UCLA chemists synthesize narrow ribbons of graphene using only light and heat</a>
								 </li></ul>
				<a href="http://newsroom.ucla.edu/" class="bullet">Enter Newsroom</a>
